const schemaScripts = ["{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"name\":\"Shower Tile Installation Sacramento\",\"provider\":{\"@type\":\"LocalBusiness\",\"name\":\"Pro Tiling\",\"telephone\":\"(916) 555-0100\"},\"areaServed\":{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Sacramento\"},\"description\":\"Custom shower tile installation in Sacramento including walk-in showers, tub surrounds, bench seats, niches, and full waterproofing systems.\",\"serviceType\":\"Shower Tile Installation\"}"];
const contentHtml = "<section class=\"page-hero\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"page-hero__content\">\n          <nav class=\"page-hero__breadcrumb\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\">\n            <a href=\"/\">Home</a><span>\u203a</span><span>Shower Tile Installation Sacramento</span>\n          </nav>\n          <h1>Shower Tile Installation in Sacramento, CA</h1>\n          <p>Custom shower tile built for beauty and longevity. Walk-in showers, tub surrounds, and wet rooms \u2014 all waterproofed and tiled to the highest standard.</p>\n          <div class=\"page-hero__cta\">\n            <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">Get a Free Estimate</a>\n            <a href=\"tel:9165550100\" class=\"btn btn--outline\">Call (916) 555-0100</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"service-content\">\n          <div class=\"content-body\">\n            <span class=\"section-label\">Shower Tile Specialists</span>\n            <h2>Custom Shower Tile That Actually Lasts</h2>\n            <p>Shower tile fails for one reason: improper waterproofing. Grout cracks, caulk peels, water gets into the substrate, mold follows. We've been brought in to fix failed shower installs throughout Sacramento that were only a few years old \u2014 and the cause is always the same. Corners were cut on the waterproofing.</p>\n            <p>We don't cut corners. Every shower we build starts with a full waterproofing system \u2014 Schluter Kerdi or a comparable membrane \u2014 installed across every surface, every transition, every corner. The tile on top is the beautiful part. The waterproofing underneath is why it lasts.</p>\n\n            <img class=\"content-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600566752355-35792bedcfea?w=900&q=80\" alt=\"Custom walk-in shower tile installation in Sacramento \u2014 large format wall tile\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" />\n\n            <h2>Shower Tile Services We Offer</h2>\n\n            <h3>Walk-In Shower Tile Installation</h3>\n            <p>Zero-entry, curbless, and curbed walk-in showers are our most popular Sacramento shower project. We tile floors, walls, and ceiling where applicable \u2014 and we build in the features that make a shower truly functional: linear drains, teak benches, recessed niches, and waterproof lighting cutouts.</p>\n\n            <h3>Tub Surround Tile</h3>\n            <p>Replacing that dated one-piece tub surround with real tile is one of the highest-ROI bathroom updates you can make. We demo the old surround, waterproof properly, and install your chosen tile \u2014 whether that's classic white subway or book-matched marble slabs.</p>\n\n            <h3>Shower Pan / Floor Tile</h3>\n            <p>Shower floors require slope to drain properly and anti-slip tiles for safety. We slope our mortar beds to the correct pitch, choose tiles appropriate for wet floor applications, and keep grout joints clean and sealed. No standing water. No slipping.</p>\n\n            <h3>Shower Niches & Built-Ins</h3>\n            <p>A properly waterproofed and tiled niche is a detail that elevates the whole shower. We frame, waterproof, and tile niches in a variety of sizes \u2014 single, double, and full-column \u2014 with accent or contrasting tile if desired.</p>\n\n            <h3>Wet Room Installation</h3>\n            <p>A true wet room \u2014 where the entire bathroom floor is tiled and waterproofed \u2014 is becoming a popular request in Sacramento luxury homes. We design and build wet room systems with full tanked waterproofing, linear drainage, and seamless floor-to-wall tile transitions.</p>\n\n            <h2>Waterproofing: Our Non-Negotiable Standard</h2>\n            <p>We won't tile over a substrate that isn't properly waterproofed. Every shower we build gets:</p>\n            <ul>\n              <li>Cement backer board or foam tile backer on all wet walls</li>\n              <li>Full sheet waterproofing membrane across all surfaces</li>\n              <li>Sealed seams, corners, and transitions \u2014 the failure points most contractors skip</li>\n              <li>Pre-tile flood test where applicable</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>This adds time and cost compared to cutting corners \u2014 and it's exactly why our showers don't leak.</p>\n\n            <h2>Serving Sacramento Shower Tile Projects Region-Wide</h2>\n            <p>We've completed custom shower tile installations in Sacramento, Elk Grove, Roseville, Folsom, Natomas, Rancho Cordova, and throughout the greater region. Whether you're in a condo in Midtown or a custom home in El Dorado Hills, we'll come out and give you an honest estimate.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"faq\">\n              <h2 style=\"margin-bottom:8px;\">Shower Tile Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"faq-item\">\n                <button class=\"faq-item__question\">How long does a shower tile installation take? <span class=\"faq-item__icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg></span></button>\n                <div class=\"faq-item__answer\"><p>A standard walk-in shower tile installation takes 4\u20136 days: demo and waterproofing on day 1\u20132, tile setting on days 2\u20134, then cure time before grouting on day 5\u20136. Custom showers with niches, benches, and multiple tile types take a bit longer. We'll give you a specific schedule before we start.</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"faq-item\">\n                <button class=\"faq-item__question\">What's the best tile for a shower floor? <span class=\"faq-item__icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"5\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"19\"/><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/></svg></span></button>\n                <div class=\"faq-item__answer\"><p>For shower floors, smaller tiles (2x2, penny round, 3x3 mosaic) provide more grout lines which create natural texture and traction. Porcelain with a rated slip coefficient is our standard recommendation. We always advise against large-format tile on shower floors for safety reasons.</p></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <aside class=\"service-sidebar\">\n            <div class=\"sidebar-card\">\n              <h3>Get a Free Estimate</h3>\n              <p style=\"font-size:0.875rem;margin-bottom:18px;\">We'll assess your shower project and give you a detailed, written estimate at no charge.</p>\n              <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn btn--primary\" style=\"width:100%;justify-content:center;\">Request a Quote</a>\n              <a href=\"tel:9165550100\" class=\"btn btn--outline-dark\" style=\"width:100%;justify-content:center;margin-top:10px;\">Call (916) 555-0100</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sidebar-card\">\n              <h3>Every Shower Includes</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Full waterproofing membrane</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Floor & wall tile</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Sealed grout</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Proper floor slope</li>\n                <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Niche option available</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sidebar-card\">\n              <h3>Related Services</h3>\n              <div class=\"sidebar-links\">\n                <a href=\"/bathroom-tile-sacramento\">\u2192 Bathroom Tile Remodeling</a>\n                <a href=\"/tile-installation-sacramento\">\u2192 Tile Installation</a>\n                <a href=\"/backsplash-installation-sacramento\">\u2192 Kitchen Backsplash</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </aside>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-band\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"cta-band__inner\">\n          <h2>Build the shower you've always wanted \u2014 <em>done right</em>.</h2>\n          <div class=\"cta-band__actions\">\n            <a href=\"tel:9165550100\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">(916) 555-0100</a>\n            <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn btn--outline\">Free Estimate</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>";
